ComicInfo.Summary: I had no idea that she was one of them. She was hot ? she had a killer body, stacked and ripped. A gym girl. I was thinking "Okay" until I saw her face pierced. She's just sitting there, minding her own business, eating a plate of eggs. When that guy whistled at her, she turned into an animal. Leapt out of her seat and punched him - clean through the wall. Killed him with a slap. That was when I knew everything had changed
